sequenceDiagram
  participant Sensor as Motion Sensor
  participant Node as ESP32 Node
  participant Broker as MQTT Broker
  participant Backend as Node.js Backend
  participant UI as React Dashboard

  Sensor->>Node: Motion detected
  Node->>Node: Update local state and RGB
  Node->>Broker: Publish telemetry/state
  Broker->>Backend: Forward message
  Backend->>Backend: Store and process
  Backend->>UI: Push live update
